1 A Little Survey

Here are just a few questions so I can get to know you and so you can get practice submitting an assignment in Canvas. For each question, insert your answer underneath. Make sure each answer is at the minimum a complete sentence with correctly spelled words and correct puncuation. Half the points in this assignment depend on your picture and name being correct!! Be sure to put your photo in the AAA_Owner_Info folder and call it My_photo.jpg after first renaming the current one to Koala.jpg .

1.1 Where are you now?

What row are you in, front,middle or back? Do you usually choose a similiar row in other classes? What is the computer number where you are sitting? How on a scale of 1 to 10 (1=low, 10=high) How you feel about periodic seat re-assignment, say how and why. Teams, have you ever worked on one in a class setting?

1.1.1 my answer

I am sitting in the middle of the class. No, I usually sit in the front, because I forget my glasses sometimes and cant see the board from afar. I am a solid 5. I dont like to move around if Im already comfortable, however, if I dont like the people who are sitting near or around me I dont mind if my seat is reassigned.I have worked on a team in class setting.

1.2 Others and You?

What name do you prefer to be called by your classmates and instructor, if your buddys call you something but you want me to call you something else - what would that be?

1.2.1 my answer

I just go by my governement name Gloria.

1.3 Aspirations?

What do you want to achieve in life? What college subject do you think would be of the greatest interest to you? What degree or certificate are you trying to achieve?

1.3.1 my answer

Honestly, I just want to travel the world and have a cute little family with some human babies and lots of fur babies. Greatest interest to me is Criminal Justice. I am trying to achieve my Bachelors Degree in Science Nursing.

1.4 Past adventures?

Have you ever gone to foreign countries, if so which ones, if not Where might you go in the future? Have you ever been in the military, if so which branch, if not which branch would you choose if you got drafted, and why?

1.4.1 my answer

The only foregin country Ive gone to is Mexico, but I have traveled alot within the US. I will be going to the Philipines in February 2020. Im praying I dont ever have to get drafted, I might just have to draw a branch name from a hat if that day ever comes.

1.5 Why are you taking Math 115?

What grade do you need to attain in stats to not upset your future plans, What is your plan?

1.5.1 my answer

Preferably, I am aiming for an A but I would settle for a B. My plan is to get my degree to become a Registered Nurse.

1.6 Homework Help and Getting around?

On a scale of 1 to 10, where 1 is a total dummy (doesnt know a mouse from a keyboard) and 10 is a complete geek (knows computer stuff in and out) How do you rate yourself? Do you have a computer you can use at home? If so, what kind is it (windows, Apple, Linux)? Do you have internet access at home?
How do you get to class? Are there issues that limit when you can be at the college?Where and when did you attend high school? Do you currently have a job?

1.6.1 my answer

I would say Im a low 7, Im proficient in computers and I work on a computer all day, but I feel like I still have alot to learn. Yes I do have internet access at hom and I do have a computer at home, windows and an apple. My mom and I share a car, but we always try our best to work around each others schedule. I went to high school here in Lancaster and I graduated from Eastside High School in 2014. i do have a job, I work as the Head of Marketing for Marro Real Estate.
